<h2 class="bold font-l">Hanging up on the Council</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Female Commander Shepard repeatedly hanging up on the Citadel Council mid-conversation. (Video by YouTuber Taina Pereira) </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/RudelyHangingUp" class='trope-example-link'>Rudely Hanging Up</a></p>
